title: Ep. #136 | Catching Up: JIUNG and KEEHO of P1Harmony
description:
JIUNG & KEEHO of P1Harmony catch up with Eric Nam during their month-long trip to the States! Learn about what they've been up to in Los Angeles and their honest feelings as they approach their 1 year anniversary. Also, the boys spill the truth about the infamous FNC dance studio ghost... Yikes!
